sub_title: Dutch music producer & record label owner.
summary:
Bastiaan de Nooijer, also known as Piece Wise is a 25-year-old Dutch music producer born in Spain and raised in Africa. Piece Wise has spent the majority of his life living in Africa, in countries such as Cameroon, Senegal, Mozambique & Mali where he has gained valuable life experiences. His musical journey began in 2012 when he first experimented with electronic music production. Over time, Piece Wise has developed his unique sound and has tied his main focus to electronic dance music. 

Piece Wise has released music on established labels such as Loudkult, We Are Diamond & Strange Fruits. Next to his music, Piece Wise dedicates his time professionally to curating various Spotify playlists, with his main goal being able to share his musical preferences & promoting, upcoming talented artists. With the launch of his own record label "Setting Sail Records", Piece Wise takes an independent path regarding his own music and focuses on the branding & releases of other artists.

Piece Wise strives to share his passion with the world. By doing so, he aims to positively impact people's lives. He finds it of utmost importance to stay engaged with his fan base, and this clearly shows. 

Piece Wise has amassed over 76,000,000+ streams on Spotify, reaching 182 countries and over 10,000,000+ unique listeners.  

Featured On:
- Setting Sail Records

Want to contact Piece Wise?
- Send in an email at: piecewisee@gmail.com
